text: Jennifer Corbet (born May 27, 1965) is an American rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Jackson Hole, Wyoming
